Definition: occupied with or fond of the pleasures of good company
Example: a convivial atmosphere at the reunion; a woman of convivial nature; he was a real good-time Charlie
Synonyms: noun, attribute, conviviality, good-time, occupied, with, or, fond, of, the, pleasures, good, company, a, atmosphere, at, reunion, woman, nature, he, was, real, Charlie
Category: adj.all
